---
title: Salisbury Steak-Style Beef Patties and Mash with Shallot Gravy and Apple Salad
description: We're  sticking to a classic here with  ground beef patties! A shallot gravy is poured over top and a creamy mash and refreshing side salad come alongside. The result is hearty, tasty and balanced — all in one meal!
